flowchart LR
    A[Ranked candidates] --> B[Orchestrator agent]

    B --> C{Directives parse and validate?}
    C -- No --> D[Repair feedback to orchestrator]
    D --> B
    C -- Yes --> E[Directive list]

    E --> F[Component question agent per directive]
    F --> G{Questions parse and validate?}
    G -- No --> H[Repair feedback to component agent]
    H --> F
    G -- Yes --> I[Accepted question sections]

    I --> J{Any directive failed?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Redistribute failed count to unused candidates]
    K --> F
    J -- No --> L[Merge all agent outputs]
    L --> M[Finalize quiz artifacts]
